changeLocale

public void changeLocale(javax.faces.event.ActionEvent event)
Handles a change of the current locale.

This implementation disable setters because of a bug of <p:wizard> component that always set properties for their checkboxes components as false when submitting the form. Moreover this implementation also localize the item 'All' of the 'Category' combo in the filter's panel of the 'Add questions' dialog because submitting form is not enough to localize it.

Parameters:
event - Action event
